profile.primary_concern: fear of stigma from community and potential side effects

context: A 30-year-old Kenyan woman is recovering from past trauma related to a health crisis. This experience has made her anxious about accessing healthcare, particularly PrEP, as she fears stigma and judgment from her community. She feels hopeful about protecting her health but is also worried about the side effects and how others will perceive her use of PrEP.
example_questions_clean: Ninafikiria kuhusu PrEP, na ningependa kujua ni nini muhimu kujua kabla ya kuanza.
Je, ni dalili zipi za kawaida za PrEP ambazo watu wanapaswa kuwa nazo akilini?
Naweza kupata wapi taarifa zaidi kuhusu vitu vyote vya PrEP?
Je, kuna njia za kufikia PrEP bila kukabiliwa na unyanyapaa katika jamii yangu?
Ninapohisi wasiwasi kuhusu kutumia PrEP, ni hatua gani ninazoweza kuchukua ili kujiimarisha kiakili?
Ni vipi PrEP inaweza kusaidia katika kuzuia maambukizi ya HIV baada ya tukio hatari?
